	(text "IO0 and IO2 are used to configure the booting mode\n\nIO5 (aka MDTI) (when 0) switches the internal\nlogic level from 3V3 to 1V8\n\nIO15 (aka MDTO) (when 0) disables debug \nlogging during boot"
